{"tid":590754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地方人妻脫衣挺普丁　女團「彈粗奶」吸票","createTime":"2018-03-13T02:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T03:01:51.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"358893a5c1d8482ab23644732ab0d50d6c41d87d","tid":590754,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:20:53.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯將在本周日舉行總統大選，外界預料現任總統普丁，應該「躺著選」就會贏，本屆普丁若當選，將是他的第4任任期，繼續邁向他的大帝之路。而這次普丁的競選策略中，沒有大打文宣廣告，反而是一堆支持者自掏腰包幫普丁做文宣，當中不乏裸體露奶攻勢。<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，繼先前《Maxim》雜誌啟用辣模為普丁拍攝宣傳廣告，現在有一名地方議員人妻戴洛娃(Yulya Dyatlova)，率領其他8名人妻與女子，全身脫光光，僅用一標語布條遮住重點部位，布條上寫著「我會去投票」，表示要用行動來支持普丁。<br />\n另外一個女團「Fabrika」則是大唱《Vova Vova》歌頌普丁，影片中不時看到普丁的照片，女團成員也大唱：「你好帥，我最愛的老闆，只有他，我的神，我要嫁給他！」全曲旋律超洗腦，就是要大家一起來投普丁。而且MV中還不時給女團員們的胸部有特寫鏡頭，更有「彈粗奶」的畫面。<br />\n報導指出，這次普丁勝券在握，最後民調出爐有高達69%的支持率，相信他躺著選就會贏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180313/640_7c898370c0ac1a90b4116dd52e55e68e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180313%2F640_7c898370c0ac1a90b4116dd52e55e68e.jpg&h=8c789a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180313/640_ea5c66e78d0db3bd028c9dd4b132e70b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180313%2F640_ea5c66e78d0db3bd028c9dd4b132e70b.jpg&h=bcb1f7fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180313/640_87f5dc6981619e988780981730448b0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180313%2F640_87f5dc6981619e988780981730448b0e.jpg&h=7032c469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 投完是否可以同地方人妻"},{"pid":"07463f4846fbc66f64a3ecb81e0b7050c82052c6","tid":590754,"uid":35430,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/13/104534_8af39b10d083d38a86183c2b9c5e46cf.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F13%2F104534_8af39b10d083d38a86183c2b9c5e46cf.JPG&h=5475164a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"276bae85db4a0db0a144f88aee83e189e16b24b4","tid":590754,"uid":4036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T02:52:09.000Z","msg":"片呢"},{"pid":"953186ca1233cd43784972ee93710ee1cd7ea7f9","tid":590754,"uid":136061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T03:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}